    public class GoogleCastRenderer
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.appscend.media.renderers.IVeeplayRenderer
    A Veeplay renderer implementation to be used with Google Cast devices Normally, this class will be instantiated automatically by the Veeplay orchestrator and should not be used directly.
